# Firebase client config — committed so CI (App Distribution) can build.
# These are NOT secrets (client API keys are public by design). The
# service-account key (server send-key) is NEVER committed — it lives in a
# GitHub secret.
#   **/google-services.json      (committed)
#   lib/firebase_options.dart    (committed)
**/GoogleService-Info.plist
*-firebase-adminsdk-*.json
